  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BEAT CHAMPION IS NOT JUST ANOTHER VR RHYTHM GAME</h2>Beat Champion was designed from the ground up to challenge you in ways never seen before in a VR rhythm game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >4 COLORS</h2>Why do other games stop at 2 colors? We have no idea, so we made one with 4. Toggle between 2 colors per hand to match the color of the note blocks. You also have to punch the notes with force! The harder you hit, the more points you get!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922190/extras/8b8856de859c0a254e589d8a6075d25c.poster.avif?t=1592310725\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922190/extras/8b8856de859c0a254e589d8a6075d25c.webm?t=1592310725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922190/extras/8b8856de859c0a254e589d8a6075d25c.mp4?t=1592310725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >VANISHING NOTES</h2>If you like a challenge then you'll LOVE vanishing notes. Vanishing notes spawn, quickly fly away, and then reappear just before you have to hit them.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922190/extras/472e4b75d476e958d95bc645a1223ff2.poster.avif?t=1592310725\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922190/extras/472e4b75d476e958d95bc645a1223ff2.webm?t=1592310725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922190/extras/472e4b75d476e958d95bc645a1223ff2.mp4?t=1592310725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >4 DIRECTIONS</h2>Immerse yourself the way VR was intended, in 360 degree space. Notes spawn from 4 directions. Tracks and arrows show you which direction you have to face.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922190/extras/99dc731e03ea3b8a348401798297a837.poster.avif?t=1592310725\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922190/extras/99dc731e03ea3b8a348401798297a837.webm?t=1592310725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922190/extras/99dc731e03ea3b8a348401798297a837.mp4?t=1592310725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MODDING</h2>Beat Champion is completely moddable. Using the free Editor Tool DLC, you can create your own songs, visuals, and note hit sounds. Share them and import what others have created!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922190/extras/90098edafb0e5258ce9dc9e30c33fd6e.poster.avif?t=1592310725\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922190/extras/90098edafb0e5258ce9dc9e30c33fd6e.webm?t=1592310725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922190/extras/90098edafb0e5258ce9dc9e30c33fd6e.mp4?t=1592310725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>4 colors, 4 directions, vanishing notes<br></li><li>Hit notes with force! Simply holding your hands out and not punching will cause you to miss.<br></li><li>Create songs, color palettes, change note colors and note hit sounds with the DLC<br></li><li>LIV supported</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BEAT CHAMPION IS NOT JUST ANOTHER VR RHYTHM GAME</h2>Beat Champion was designed from the ground up to challenge you in ways never seen before in a VR rhythm game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >4 COLORS</h2>Why do other games stop at 2 colors? We have no idea, so we made one with 4. Toggle between 2 colors per hand to match the color of the note blocks. You also have to punch the notes with force! The harder you hit, the more points you get!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922190/extras/8b8856de859c0a254e589d8a6075d25c.poster.avif?t=1592310725\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922190/extras/8b8856de859c0a254e589d8a6075d25c.webm?t=1592310725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922190/extras/8b8856de859c0a254e589d8a6075d25c.mp4?t=1592310725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >VANISHING NOTES</h2>If you like a challenge then you'll LOVE vanishing notes. Vanishing notes spawn, quickly fly away, and then reappear just before you have to hit them.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922190/extras/472e4b75d476e958d95bc645a1223ff2.poster.avif?t=1592310725\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922190/extras/472e4b75d476e958d95bc645a1223ff2.webm?t=1592310725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922190/extras/472e4b75d476e958d95bc645a1223ff2.mp4?t=1592310725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >4 DIRECTIONS</h2>Immerse yourself the way VR was intended, in 360 degree space. Notes spawn from 4 directions. Tracks and arrows show you which direction you have to face.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922190/extras/99dc731e03ea3b8a348401798297a837.poster.avif?t=1592310725\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922190/extras/99dc731e03ea3b8a348401798297a837.webm?t=1592310725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922190/extras/99dc731e03ea3b8a348401798297a837.mp4?t=1592310725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MODDING</h2>Beat Champion is completely moddable. Using the free Editor Tool DLC, you can create your own songs, visuals, and note hit sounds. Share them and import what others have created!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922190/extras/90098edafb0e5258ce9dc9e30c33fd6e.poster.avif?t=1592310725\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922190/extras/90098edafb0e5258ce9dc9e30c33fd6e.webm?t=1592310725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/922190/extras/90098edafb0e5258ce9dc9e30c33fd6e.mp4?t=1592310725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>4 colors, 4 directions, vanishing notes<br></li><li>Hit notes with force! Simply holding your hands out and not punching will cause you to miss.<br></li><li>Create songs, color palettes, change note colors and note hit sounds with the DLC<br></li><li>LIV supported</li></ul>",
